formThreeBId.notesToCertificate:
This certificate is being issued for RERA compliance for the Company AAKRUTS COMMOTRADE PRIVATE LIMITED and for Project Called KARMABHUMI DREAM CITY and is based on the records and documents produced before me and explanations provided to me by the management of the Company Based on the Verification of Books of Accounts till Dated 30.09.2022				
The Bank account of the company is with Bank of Baroda Tithal Road Branch but in the certificate it is prefilled as Bulsar Main Branch which was at the time of registration and now it has been changed which unit will file for correction.The Company is also depositing the proceeds of this project into escrow account no. 174102000000906 with Bank of Baroda and OD account no. 1914505926 with Kotak Mahindra Bank. In the account stated above receipts/payments of other projects covered/not covered under RERA are also included.The Plot number allotted in approved plan is different from the plot number submitted in RERA and as per explanation given by the Director of the Company application for revised plan has been submitted to the authorities but has not been approved yet. So the number of units as per Plan and as per RERA are different. We have not verified the KYC documents , Contracts and registered sale deed of the parties. The Company is in default of repayment to the Bank as on date.
